nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: Ultra-realistic close-up portrait of a 20-year-old young woman with long, wavy red hair cascading over her shoulders, each strand catching the light with vivid copper and auburn tones. The shot captures her from just above the eyebrows to below the chin, filling the frame with her face. Her pale, freckled skin is rendered in extreme detail, with visible pores, fine facial hairs, and subtle texture variations. Her green eyes shimmer with intricate iris detail, reflecting soft window light. The lighting is natural and diffused, creating gentle shadows that define the contours of her cheekbones, nose, and jawline. She wears minimal makeup—only a hint of mascara and a soft nude lip—allowing her natural beauty to stand out. The depth of field is razor-thin, keeping her eyes and skin texture perfectly sharp while the background melts into a smooth, blurred gradient. The mood is intimate and calm, as if she is lost in thought. The high-resolution detail should reveal micro-reflections in her eyes, the natural texture of her lips, and the way light plays across each hair strand. Shot with a Canon EOS R5 and a 100mm f/2.8 macro lens, 8K resolution, cinematic color grading.
